    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接续第一季的内容，展开新的冒险！新的朋友和敌人、危险和奖励在等着你。其中既包括了主线战役的扩充内容，也不乏独立的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Last Sarkorians</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/458594ed023ef1f55d8f3b8cd6e329f1.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1200 height=674 /></span>为骑士指挥官的队伍准备的新战役即将推出，随之而来的还有一个新的可选职业：变化万千的化形师！这个可靠的斗士能够化为各种野兽的形貌，让你的队伍变得更强。你还将深入探究旧萨阔力失落的秘密。说不定……甚至还能收获一段超越时间本身的爱情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/56d7d6f306c51d846ec0e2b188be1f8d.poster.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1170 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/56d7d6f306c51d846ec0e2b188be1f8d.webm?t=1757500291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Lord of Nothing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/cb12039b1ee3fb6ca4467c83452894a4.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1200 height=674 /></span>这部新的独立战役将续写《浴灰而行》留下的悬念。一名新的恶魔领主率领成群结队的冰冷爪牙，从深渊之底倾巢而出。骑士指挥官正在其他地方奋战，而一群没有神话之力的普通冒险者，又能做些什么来拯救世界呢？本扩展剧情提供6-7小时的故事内容，可供独立游玩，也可以使用《浴灰而行》存档中的英雄。在完成此战役后，主线战役中将开放一个全新的地城，供骑士指挥官探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/0c53956e86a43d0e60534e2e5919bbcf.poster.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1170 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/0c53956e86a43d0e60534e2e5919bbcf.webm?t=1757500291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Dance of Masks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/8a5a3a5259174545d86686accab2ceb1.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1200 height=674 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >假面之舞是《开拓者：正义之怒》的第六部也是第2季票最后一部豪华DLC，是写给骑士指挥官与诸位忠诚同伴的最后一封情书。召集你的所有同伴，返回漫漫长路启始之地：坎娜布利，这座饱经劫难、浴火重生的城市。出席一场庆典，庆祝您的胜利，与朋友和挚爱加深交情，欣赏焰火表演……并挫败试图大煞风景的恶棍们的计划！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/238ce2da236c88678d4e72838be5d20c.poster.avif?t=1757500291\" width=1170 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145870/extras/238ce2da236c88678d4e72838be5d20c.webm?t=1757500291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
